AUDIO: 'This solo real estate agent posts a brand new video for every single new listing in his market. And the thing is, he hasn\'t been on camera in over 6 months. Instead, he uses an AI avatar of himself, one reusable listing prompt, and of course, HeyGen to turn new'

[00:12] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'listing details into finished social media videos in just minutes. And in this video, I\'m going to show you the workflow step-by-step and how you can do it for yourself. And before we start, if tutorials like this help you guys out,'

