AUDIO: 'once the script feels right, copy it and save it into a safe spot for now. Because in just a second, we\'re going to be using it to make our video script inside of HeyGen. And now, inside HeyGen, there\'s actually a couple different ways you can create the video. The first one\'s the manual route, but'

