[06:18] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'shot. But now, especially for our scenario, this is where HeyGen C Dance feature can really come in handy because now you\'re not just limited to static photos. If you have listing photos of a room or a hallway, you can use C Dance to turn that still image into a moving'

[06:30] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'shot. For example, you can pick the first frame and the last frame of a photo. Say the first photo is an angle of the room, and the second photo is a slightly farther away angle, or the first photo is the start of a hallway, and the last photo is the end of it. We'

[06:43] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'can let C Dance create that middle motion. So, now it can feel like the camera is actually moving through that space. And now that\'s going to give us a super smooth and clean walk-through shot that nobody even needed to go to the property and film. And you could use'

[06:55] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'this for any single room of the house. You can also just use C Dance for extra B-roll, like a cinematic shot moving through a modern living room, or slow camera move down a hallway, or just a clean exterior shot of the home. Then you can bring those clips back into the'

